{"tid":1538504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔可以就咁放棄","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:06.000Z","uid":230905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d49fa3efb2c31770084d476524ece3464e0744c","tid":1538504,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"呢三個月嚟，我地班手足死既死，傷既傷，拉既拉，依家淋病話宣佈撤回咋，係宣佈！！<br />\n仲記唔記得倪老先生講過D乜，唔記得請重溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=75FV2lvEw2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D75FV2lvEw2U&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=be668fa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=75FV2lvEw2U</a> <br />\n如果依家接受呢個結果，真係對唔住為咗呢場運動而死既手足！<br />\n班狗咁撚腐敗，根本就權力過大，當香港人係曱甴，你地見過佢地既罪行，可以當無事發生過?<br />\n醫管局個高永文又係奶共，班教畜又係，你地接受你地既下一代要受咁既教育制度咩。<br />\n當一切回復正常，每日150個就繼續，啲大陸閪又係落嚟整污糟我地個家，你地可以忍受咩，依家酒店咁撚平住到一晚，啲福建幫既酒樓一間執一間，呢啲係班手足用血汗換取返嚟，革命就係需要流血，香港人唔好再階段性勝利，一日共產黨係度，一日香港人都唔會有好日子過，班共產黨只係分別有無利益可圖，用完即棄，班牛屎佬仲唔識驚，共產黨打度嚟，就收佢地既丁權，果陣喊都無謂，果陣至嚟反抗，乜柒都太遲，依家香港人已經覺醒咗好多，但我地唔要做覺醒者，係要做變革者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/150956_62e276da37eb84253c4e658c5f621926.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F150956_62e276da37eb84253c4e658c5f621926.png&h=83165418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cd44c74f05b8471afdf056530ae50e14cd85cf4","tid":1538504,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bca4f75b7143c382d00e93ef560dd58595ce3e67","tid":1538504,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"2278b34c846958d941b0d8b2396aad44ed2660cd","tid":1538504,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e98bfd7f7426a71f04386ff4044d07a9f253678","tid":1538504,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:34.0